OL,12,CG1970FThe 1970 FA Cup Final Replay at
OL,13,FOld Trafford, Manchester airs on BBC
OL,14,FOne/ITV. Chelsea beat Leeds United 2-1.
OL,15,FThe match attracted an audience of
OL,16,F28.49m, making it the sixth
OL,17,Fmost-watched TV special event in UK
OL,18,Fhistory.
